          .icons
            a
              img.custom-icon(src="images/cc.jfif")
          a Adobe CC Projects
          p Here is some work I have done in Adobe Illustrator and Photoshop. The first 5 are icons and the last image is an Under Armor ad that I recreated.
        .portfolio-item.adobe-item.first-transition#zion
          iframe( width="100%" height="100%" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VEohGJnFIXg?rel=0" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen )
        .portfolio-item.adobe-item.first-transition
            img(src='images/headphones.png' alt='over ear headphones')
        .portfolio-item.adobe-item.second-transition
            img(src='images/speaker.png' alt='speaker')
        .portfolio-item.adobe-item.second-transition
            img(src='images/microphone.png' alt='stick microphone')
        .portfolio-item.adobe-item.third-transition
            img(src='images/old-microphone.png' alt='old school microphone')
        .portfolio-item.adobe-item.third-transition
            img(src='images/earbuds.png' alt='earbuds')
        .portfolio-item.adobe-item.fourth-transition
            img(src='images/climber.jpg' alt='woman climbing')
    .container-full
      #contact
        form(action="/sendEmail" class="contact" method="post")
          h2 Shoot me a message at
          p
            a(href="mailto: mikenishiguchi@gmail.com") mikenishiguchi@gmail.com
          input(name="subject" class="emailSubject" type="text" placeholder="subject" required)
          textarea(type="text" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Your message..." required)
          button.btn.btn-block(type='submit' class="blueBtn") Send

